Ezekiel Milquetoast needs your help! He has lost a simple trinket
that he was going to use to conduct a magical experiment. Some
small, annoying goblins jumped him in his courtyard and stole
it because - well, goblins like to do that. Seek him out
and help him find his lost trinket.

Rumor has it, he resides in his home somewhere north of
Darkwind City proper.


** This quest must be completed before reaching level 10 **

